author: andreasmyth
msg: Factoring out more functionality  common to client and server binding.

Moving it into new classes AbstractBindingBase (implements org.objectweb.celtix.bindings.BindingBase) and AbstractBindingImpl (implements javax.xml.ws.Binding). This eliminates the need for marshal and unmarshal APIs in both AbstractClientBinding and AbstractServerBinding.
